#: ../../source/docs/open_bil_bip_bsq_files.rst:49
msgid ""
"Unzip and extract the .bsq file. On Windows, you may use the excellent "
"`7-Zip utility <http://www.7-zip.org/>`_ to read and extract .gz file. You "
